moji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:22:40.000Z","msg":"當我睇完你個帖，我好唔開心，我忍唔住，所以決定寫呢番心聲&hellip;我想問樓主你知唔知你自己做緊乜！？你帖嘅內容完全有害無益不知所謂，我真係唔明點解依家討論區搞成咁，咁多你D咁嘅人！你有冇諗過你開呢個帖會令人好不安，令幾多人受到傷害，點解你要咁做！？你父母可能在痛哭，痛恨你點解會變成咁，而佢地會問個天點解會生左你呢種人危害社會，佢地一定寧可生一個智障人士，都唔希望有你咁嘅衰仔&hellip;你嘅行為係完全浪費所有對你有期望嘅人嘅希望，浪費互聯網資源；浪費所有睇左你個帖嘅人寶貴嘅時間&hellip;你有冇諗過你可以用你發帖嘅時間用嘅做吓義工或做D對社會有貢獻嘅事；少D打飛機，孝順父母呢？"},{"pid":"4891ce8fa804a17a64651edcd32d7388c175ce61","tid":2435223,"uid":133185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T11:04:25.000Z","msg":"飲緊水差啲瀆撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f5f9e03414924bb530df272f5d2098912172547","tid":2435223,"uid":210729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4891ce8fa804a17a64651edcd32d7388c175ce61","tid":2435223,"uid":133185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T11:04:25.000Z","msg":"飲緊水差啲瀆撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T11:29:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢哋都唔識欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f311f6749836bafbce1d5931aa9bc020f0baffc3","tid":2435223,"uid":133185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f5f9e03414924bb530df272f5d2098912172547","tid":2435223,"uid":210729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4891ce8fa804a17a64651edcd32d7388c175ce61","tid":2435223,"uid":133185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T11:04:25.000Z","msg":"飲緊水差啲瀆撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T11:29:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢哋都唔識欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\